@errors {401: Authorization failed. Please supply a valid `DeepL-Auth-Key` via the `Authorization` header., 403: Authorization failed. Please supply a valid `DeepL-Auth-Key` via the `Authorization` header., 429: Too many requests. Please wait and resend your request., 500: Internal error., 503: Resource currently unavailable. Try again later., 529: Too many requests. Please wait and resend your request.}

